t: "And do not say to what your tongues/languages/speeches describes/categorizes the lies/defiance/falsehood, that (is) permitted/allowed, and that (is) forbidden .\" To fabricate/cut and split on (about) God the lies/denials/falsehood: \"That those who fabricate/cut and split on (about) God the lies/denials/falsehood do not succeed/win"